node.text:
Have you been buying and selling on @ebay? These folks were coming up in #Dallas with pairs bought on eBay with the #AuthenticityGuarantee and sold at the event, while others purchased at the event and sold on eBay with 0% seller fees.
.
🙏 Thanks @patperezgolf for coming through and showing off this dope AJ1 “Board of Governors” aka “Black & Royal Homage To Home”.
.
🎤 Shout out @marissaehill on the intro.

node.text:
#SneakerCon #Dallas was not only our comeback event but it was our biggest event to date! @ebaysneakers joined us in a big way bringing the #AuthenticityGuarantee to our live marketplace.
.
More onsite authenticators than ever, thousands of attendees got free authentication services, $10k given in User Appreciation, and Live Auctions saved buyers an average of 10% off market value.
.
All this to give back to the community that started buying and selling 25 years ago on #ebay . 🙏 #silveranniversary
.
Stay tuned for our next event reveal and what #ebaysneakers has in store.

node.text:
Our collab with @bannedla sold out on Day 1 of our #BayArea event!!! For all of those who missed out we are giving you a chance to get in…
.
The collection will be available for 24 hours starting at 3pm EST / 12pm PST today via the link:
.
ruinmylife.la/collections/latest-arrivals
.
Thanks to all who came out 🙏 #sneakercon #bannedla 
.
